metadata.name: Breaking dawn
metadata.description:
- Breaking dawn -

I greet the rays of sunshine,
with no veil to cover me.
Tasting coffee we talk,
and I hide nothing from you.
Afternoon hours pass,
and I remain unclothed.
Sipping tea to pass the time,
we play games of you and me.
Dinner time arrives,
and I stay naked for you.
A promise of desert,
even sweeter is to come.
As midnight hour strikes,
your body comforts me.

1/1
